<p><b><font size=+2>Example</font></b>
<hr WIDTH="100%"></center>
<font size=+1>In this study, following example was considered as an implementation
of active index structure.</font>
<p><font size=+1>-A travel agency has a web site. They serve online reservation
and selling service for airline tickets. They work with three different
airline companies which are X, Y and Z airways. A customer browse the main
web page and he enters the desired destination and departure date to travel
with airplane. This knowledge is sent to three airline companies, which
respond if they serve for desired destination on this date and the price.
After responding, the comparison is made to determine the airline company,
which gives the cheapest price. After comparison OK message is sent to
that company to reserve the ticket.</font>
